    "body": "`is_deep_gemm_e8m0_used()` and `current_platform.is_device_capability()` are not compatible with Dynamo, causing failed compilations. This PR intends to fix this problem.\n\n### Testing\nRun inference on `Qwen/Qwen3-30B-A3B-FP8` (one of the models affected) with `VLLM_USE_DEEP_GEMM=1`.",
